{
  "stem": "8.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were taken to a very big room, and, and slept on the floor-- on a cement floor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is the first time that we were given food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, the food came in a big pot, and we had to-- there were no spoons or, or bowls to eat from.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were told that everybody has to drink from that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so we passed it around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I first tasted it, I, I could not stand it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the next time it came around to me, I, I drank it because I know if-- I knew if I didn't, I wouldn't survive.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, later on, we, we, we counted how each of us swallowed-- how many s-- s-- swallowed so we make sure that we didn't drink more than our allotted share.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My friend, who was my best friend in Hungary, she refused to drink it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I tried to beg her and, and yelled at her to drink it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she says, no, I'm not going to drink it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I said, you won't survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She says, I don't care if I don't survive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And indeed, she didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And for years, I dreamt with her running and racing together, and she falling behind.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I had such a feeling of, of guilt that I allowed her to give up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now in this place, we stayed only 10 days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And after 10 days, we were selected to work, which was a wonderful thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we were taken into the wagons again, into the cattle cars, and taken to a place called Auschwitz-- Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And Plaszow was near Krakow, and it was a family camp, where families were-- like a ghetto, and families lived together before we arrived.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
